---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="GDPR">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10">
    <a href="/app/" class="text-sm font-medium text-clinical-700 hover:underline">← App</a>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">GDPR-conscious design</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-slate mt-6 max-w-none text-slate-700">
      <p>
        We apply <strong>data minimisation</strong>: only what you need for a training logbook is stored. There is no
        marketing profile and no unnecessary tracking in this MVP.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>User control:</strong> export your data anytime; delete your account when supported. Row Level
        Security ensures each user can only access their own rows.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Processor / controller:</strong> for self-hosted or your own Supabase project, you determine the legal
        roles. For a demo deployment, document who operates the Supabase project and how trainees can contact you.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Contact:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:user6581@proton.me" class="text-clinical-700 underline">user6581@proton.me</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
